  <brief_title>Comparison of an Interscalene Nerve Block With or Without Stellate Ganglion Block for Shoulder Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of the Analgesic Effect of Levobupivacaine 0.5% Via Interscalene Nerve Block or Via Interscalene Nerve Block Combined With a Stellate Ganglion Block in Patients Undergoing Shoulder Arthroscopy With General Anaesthesia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
